  <body>
    <p id="p_ntb_dgk_54b">In <ph keyref="product"/>, custom <xref keyref="glossentry_framework"
        ><term>framework</term></xref> can be packed and deployed as an <term>add-on</term>.</p>
    <section id="packing_a_plugin_or_framework_as_an_addon">
      <title>Packing a Framework as an Add-on</title>
      <p id="p_otb_dgk_54b">This procedure is suitable for developers who want a better control over the <xref
          keyref="glossentry_plugin"><term>add-on</term></xref> package or those who want to
        automate some of the steps:<ol id="ol_ill_g4p_xlb">
          <li id="li_ptb_dgk_54b" irina="irina">Pack the <xref href="framework-customization-extending.dita">full custom
                <term>framework</term></xref> (or an extension of a framework) as a ZIP file or a
              <xref keyref="glossentry_jar"><term>Java Archive</term></xref>. Note that you should
            pack the entire root directory not just its contents.</li>
          <li conkeyref="reusables-tools/li2" id="li_qtb_dgk_54b" irina="irina"/>
          <li conkeyref="reusables-tools/li3" id="li_rtb_dgk_54b" irina="irina"/>
        </ol></p>
    </section>
